title: 527.43 SAVINGS PROVISION.
text: To the extent that sections 527.21 to 527.40, by virtue of section 527.42, paragraph (b), do not apply to transfers made in a manner prescribed in Minnesota Statutes 1984, sections 527.01 to 527.11 or to the powers, duties, and immunities conferred by transfers in that manner upon custodians and persons dealing with custodians, the repeal of Minnesota Statutes 1984, sections 527.01 to 527.11 does not affect those transfers or those powers, duties, and immunities.
